column2: SELECT   s.z,s.velDisp,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid,  ge.lgm_tot_p8#, ge.bptclass,  ge.sfr_tot_p5#, ge.specsfr_fib_p5#   gi.d4#_n,gi.d4#_n_err FROM SpecObj AS s  JOIN galSpecIndx AS gi ON s.specObjID = gi.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra AS ge ON s.specObjID = ge.specObjID  JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS sph ON s.specObjID = sph.specObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND  s.survey = &&&  AND  s.class = &&&  AND  s.snMedian_r > #  AND  s.zWARNING = #
